How to Ask Questions?

# How long vs. How long time vs. How much time vs. How many times
### "How long" == "amount of time" 
	How long have you been here?
	How long have you lived here?
	How long have you studied English?

### "How much time" == "How long" == "amount of time"
	How much time have you been here?

##### "How long" is more natural

### "How many times" == "event count"
	How many times will you watch this video?

 
